@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_nomdvz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.abs(0.55))
    v1 = wp.exp((wp.exp(v2 + 0.13) + (v0 + 0.09 + v0 + 0.13)))
    v0 = tmp
    v1 = tmp
    v1 = v2
    tmp = 0.24
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.abs(wp.sin(tmp + 0.99)))
    v2 = ((v2 - (v0 + 0.60 + v1 + 0.78)) * (0.58 * v0))
    data[tid] = v0
